schools.name: Edmundo Eddie Escobedo Sr Middle School

data.description:
Beautiful one story home located in the heart of Providence. This 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home features an open floor plan with the kitchen overlooking the family and dining rooms. Dishwasher, stove, and water heater are all new! Primary bedroom is separate from the other two bedrooms and has a slider to the backyard. * Whole home humidifier with smart thermostat ! *
Resort-like Clubhouse with great room, features pools and a workout room in a park like setting.
